BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 692.00 Tm (A local web app for monitoring OpenClaw agents and managing project tasks in a kanban board.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 678.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 678.00 Tm (It combines live agent updates, JSON-backed task operations, and Markdown sync utilities in one) Tj ET
