BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 586.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 586.00 Tm (Shows agent cards with status, model, channel, token usage, and recent activity.) Tj ET
