BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 572.00 Tm (Loads agent data by REST and refreshes it through a local WebSocket feed.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 558.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 558.00 Tm (Displays tasks in todo, in-progress, and done kanban columns.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 544.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 544.00 Tm (Creates, updates, and deletes JSON-backed tasks through backend APIs.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 530.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 530.00 Tm (Switches between projects and computes project progress summaries.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 516.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 516.00 Tm (Syncs task data between Markdown task docs and tasks/*.json.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 502.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 502.00 Tm (Watches task and subagent-related files, then broadcasts task updates to connected clients.) Tj ET
