BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 468.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 468.00 Tm (Frontend: React 18 + Vite app with Dashboard and KanbanBoard views; uses fetch plus a browser) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 456.00 Tm (WebSocket client.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 442.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 442.00 Tm (Backend: Express on port 3000 exposes agents, tasks, sync, task-doc, file-watcher, sync-lock,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 430.00 Tm (and health endpoints; a WebSocket server on port 3001 broadcasts AGENTS_UPDATE and TASK_UPDATE.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 416.00 Tm (-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 416.00 Tm (Data/services: AgentService reads OpenClaw gateway or session data; TaskService reads and writes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 404.00 Tm (tasks/<project>-tasks.json; sync services convert Markdown to JSON and generate progress docs.) Tj ET
